{"tid":1134790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心出軌】網民發萬人聯署 要求無線炒黃心穎","createTime":"2019-05-02T01:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T13:09:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e8015195760d5134987c7c8d755f6d4278f70b4c","tid":1134790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190502/_2019050206493858760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190502%2F_2019050206493858760.jpg&h=38cdb82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃心穎與許志安出軌事件轟動全城，黃心穎亦即時停工，其參演的劇集甚至安排易角重拍。有網民於上月20日開設一個名為「要求無線與黃心穎即時終止經理人合約」的Facebook專頁，發起代號「驅狐行動」聯署，冀集齊一萬人簽名後，向有關方面提出解約訴求。截至今早六時半，有610人簽署聯署。<br />\n<br />\n專頁聲明指，發起人指黃心穎身為香港小姐及公眾人物，行為對社會造成一定影響，並認為其道歉欠缺悔意，又指無線作為香港主要傳媒有相當的社會責任，若讓黃心穎在黃金時間出現，會助長歪風。聯署又作出強烈譴責，提出三項要求，分別是「即時終止無線與黃小姐經理人合約」、「考慮褫奪其2012年香港小姐亞軍資格」以及「要求黃心穎真人露面向公眾道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1491439/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1491439%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=13578711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1491439%2F&h=a1f22c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1491439/</a>"},{"pid":"527cfacf1ead73364627458bfd964f6f9ab68d1a","tid":1134790,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"人哋都杜咗歉 做乜要整死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32330503e802a5f31d8f52e5acf64686780f126f","tid":1134790,"uid":41974,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:56:39.000Z","msg":"不如聯處凌遲處死佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ac1ec81c5bd505cc4e67c2bf5e9c28119849b9","tid":1134790